      <title>SERI News October 2014</title>
      <lead>Information from the State Secretariat for Education, Research and Innovation SERI</lead>
      <text link="no">&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;EUREKA research and innovation initiative&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Development of EUREKA under Swiss presidency&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bilateral innovation cooperation under Swiss chairmanship of EUREKA&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;SMEs to gain easier access to international networks&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SwissSkills Bern 2014 and international VPET congress&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;"Well worth the effort"&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Exchange programmes for holders of VET qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The search for new exchange options for holders of VET qualifications&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;educa.ch - Education on the Net&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;"Mobile, social and game based learning" modifies traditional perceptions of classroom instruction&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Higher Education Act (HEdA)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Reading of Federal Council‘s proposed ordinance pending&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Long-term humanities project completed&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The epic Historical Dictionary of Switzerland reaches the letter Z&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Marcel Benoist Prize 2014 goes to Nicolas Gisin&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Quantum physicist receives "Swiss Nobel Prize"&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;European cooperation in education and research&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Overview of Switzerland's participation in Erasmus+ and Horizon 2020&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;50 years of European space travel&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;The European Space Agency celebrates its anniversary with an international conference in Geneva&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CERN - anniversary celebrations in Geneva&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;60 years serving science and society&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</text>
      <contact>medien@sbfi.admin.ch</contact>
